OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be cloudy across most
OL,6,Fparts with patchy rain and a fresh
OL,7,Fsouthwesterly breeze. Dry, bright and
OL,8,Fwarm towards the Moray Firth,
OL,9,FInverness and Strathspey.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry with a few bright or
OL,12,Fclear intervals near the Moray Firth
OL,13,Fand east of the Great Glen. Otherwise
OL,14,Fit will remain cloudy and breezy with
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain,
OL,18,Fheavy at times in the west. Dry with
OL,19,Fsome bright spells across Inverness
OL,20,Fand Nairn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
